<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt umb ein manung den
                                <expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ee der lantfrid czü
                                <expan>sa<ex>m</ex>men</expan> köm. Nu das als kurcz ist, so
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> wir
                                <add><expan>dary<ex>n</ex>ne</expan></add> nicht pessers, dann daz
                        ewr und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stete frewnde czü den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die wir czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantfr<ex>ide</ex></expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, kumen <app><note><q type="date">auf den nehsten samstag</q>29.03.1410</note></app> czenacht
                        <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den suntag</q>30.03.1410</note></app> gar frü gen
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Newenstat und sich
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> do miteinander
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>reden</expan>, wa von des notdurft sey, ee die
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des lantfrids dohin
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add>dahin wir die
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> also <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wöll<ex>en</ex></expan></add>. Und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>das</add> den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sweinfürt, Winsheim und
                                <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie die iren also dohin
                            <add>auch</add> schicken. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii pasche. </ab>
